The world’s biggest water fight! 😵‍💫
Songkran Festival, Thailand’s traditional New Year, is happening April 13-15, 2025 🥳
. It’s a celebration of
renewal, where water symbolizes washing away bad luck and starting fresh! Honestly it was so much fun and i felt so safe here as a woman🙆🏻‍♀️

Where to Celebrate:

Phuket - My top pick! Celebrating Songkran by the ocean just hits different. Think epic beach parties, stunning sunsets, and all-day water fights along Patong Beach!

Bangkok - If you love crazy street parties, head to Khao San Road or Silom Road for non-stop action.
